WEBVTT

00:02:57.909 --> 00:03:00.925
was like a new home.

00:03:00.925 --> 00:03:03.120
And the point of going down to

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:06.967
and living at this habitat was not to stay inside.

00:03:06.967 --> 00:03:09.566
It wasn't about living at something
the size of a school bus.

00:03:09.566 --> 00:03:12.772
It was about giving us the luxury of time

00:03:12.772 --> 00:03:15.821
outside to wander, to explore,

00:03:15.821 --> 00:03:19.704
to understand more about this oceanic final frontier.

00:03:19.704 --> 00:03:22.011
We had megafauna come and visit us.

00:03:22.011 --> 00:03:25.551
